column2: How satisfied are you from the profs
column3: Write your opinion about the faculty.

I just wanted to express my sincere appreciation for all the hard work and dedication you have put into teaching me this year. Your passion for the subject and willingness to go above and beyond to help me understand the material has made a huge impact on my learning. Your patience and kindness have also made the classroom a welcoming and supportive environment, and I am grateful for the opportunity to have you as my teacher. Thank you for everything!
